         <div type="traslation">
            <head>Translation</head>
            <p>The total of 3723 viruttams of the 94 attiyāyams of the 2 kāṇṭams is fully copied and
               completed. Honour to the illustrious (emend śra into śrī) teachers. Only the foot of
               the teacher is the refuge. The illustrious Ciṟṟampalam. On the day of the Jovian year
               Kīlaka, the month of Āvaṇi, the 29th day, the eleventh [lunar day], the constellation
               of Attam, Thursday, Pālavīrayyaṉ fully copied. The essence is Śiva (civamayyam).</p>
         </div>
